841
01:11:15,985 --> 01:11:18,453
(SCOFFlNG) Don't be ridiculous.

842
01:11:22,559 --> 01:11:24,686
Well, are you coming or not?

843
01:11:28,598 --> 01:11:29,826
Ask me nicely.

844
01:11:37,807 --> 01:11:41,573
Please, dear husband,
