947
01:20:28,437 --> 01:20:30,132
I hardly knew.

948
01:20:33,175 --> 01:20:35,609
-A good knight.
-Short, but sweet.

949
01:20:36,679 --> 01:20:39,807
I mean, he was a good knight.

950
01:20:40,383 --> 01:20:42,374
A good knight-at-arms, a soldier.

951
01:20:42,451 --> 01:20:44,783
(STAMMERlNG) Oh, yes,
