991
01:24:47,196 --> 01:24:51,724
What has 18 legs and isn't going anywhere?

992
01:24:54,770 --> 01:24:57,102
Your next move will be your last.

993
01:24:58,340 --> 01:24:59,602
Evening, friend.

994
01:25:01,644 --> 01:25:04,078
