1010
01:26:32,735 --> 01:26:35,101
If you have to ask, it's not a gift.

1011
01:26:37,206 --> 01:26:38,673
Thank you.

1012
01:27:17,212 --> 01:27:19,043
(GRUNTlNG)

1013
01:27:19,615 --> 01:27:21,173
(SCREAMlNG)

1014
01:27:24,319 --> 01:27:25,650
